2.SUMMARY: StructTreeRoot either either doesn't contain or contains more than one <Document>

1656.SUMMARY: Found circular mapping between structure types
1656.DESCRIPTION: A circular mapping between structure types is not permitted

1657.SUMMARY: A standard structure type is remapped to a non-standard type

1658.SUMMARY: StructTreeRoot entry is not present in the document catalog

1659.SUMMARY: A Structure element dictionary does not contain the P (parent) entry
1659.DESCRIPTION: Structure element dictionary shall contain the P (parent) entry
